# Streamify - Language Exchange Platform

Streamify is a modern language exchange and chat platform built with **React**, **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**. It enables users to connect, chat, and practice languages with others worldwide, featuring real-time messaging, friend requests, onboarding, and video calls.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- **User Authentication** (Sign Up, Login, Logout)
- **Profile Onboarding** (Bio, Languages, Location, Avatar)
- **Friend Requests & Notifications**
- **Real-Time Chat** (powered by [Stream Chat](https://getstream.io/chat/))
- **Video Calls** (powered by [Stream Video](https://getstream.io/video/))
- **Theme Selector** (with [DaisyUI](https://daisyui.com/) & Tailwind CSS)
- **Responsive UI** (Mobile & Desktop)
- **Modern Stack**: React 19, Vite, Zustand, React Query, Lucide Icons

