## ğŸ“„ API Endpoints

- **Auth:** `/api/auth/signup`, `/api/auth/login`, `/api/auth/logout`, `/api/auth/onboarding`, `/api/auth/me`
- **Users:** `/api/users`, `/api/users/friends`, `/api/users/friend-request/:id`, `/api/users/friend-request/:id/accept`, `/api/users/friend-request`, `/api/users/outgoing-friend-request`
- **Chat:** `/api/chat/token`

